196
00:18:51,320 --> 00:18:53,590
She still had her cellphone?

197
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,320
Yes.

198
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:57,670
Apparently, just before her death,

199
00:18:58,800 --> 00:19:03,740
