want to ask him about.

235
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:51,110
It's bad, Koiso-san!

236
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:52,550
The cursed video is real!

237
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,440
What?

238
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:56,230
